26
00:03:24,037 --> 00:03:26,414
So, you'd like to develop an app with us?

27
00:03:26,497 --> 00:03:28,750
Yes, a health app.

28
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:31,878
We would like to develop
a built-in app for QL phones that monitors

29
00:03:31,961 --> 00:03:34,047
the users' health measurements,
such as heart rate,

30
00:03:34,130 --> 00:03:36,716
blood pressure, and BMI.

31
00:03:36,799 --> 00:03:39,844
The app will send the data directly to us
at Sangkook University Hospital.

32
00:03:39,928 --> 00:03:41,387
"Exclusively"

33
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:42,931
is a better-fitting word.

34
00:03:43,932 --> 00:03:47,101
