48
00:04:29,727 --> 00:04:31,854
Healthy Life Clinic, right?

49
00:04:31,938 --> 00:04:34,107
You recently announced your plan for that,
didn't you?

50
00:04:35,066 --> 00:04:37,110
-I did.
-"Your heart rate

51
