is irregular because of your smoking.

52
00:04:41,656 --> 00:04:44,784
Okay, then. Go over
to Sangkook Smoking Cessation Clinic."

53
00:04:45,451 --> 00:04:46,619
That's what you want to do.

54
00:04:47,203 --> 00:04:49,289
Why should I help you?

55
00:04:49,998 --> 00:04:52,250
I can explain
how we will distribute profits

56
00:04:52,333 --> 00:04:54,419
generated through this app right now,
if you'd like.

57
00:04:56,838 --> 00:04:58,006
But rather than that…

58
00:04:58,548 --> 00:05:01,759
I know Chairman Hong Seong-chan
of QL Electronics

59
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:04,512
won't miss out on a great opportunity

60
00:05:04,595 --> 00:05:08,016
just because it would benefit
someone else as well.

61
00:05:08,725 --> 00:05:10,935
