an alliance with a hospital.

68
00:05:30,413 --> 00:05:32,582
The problem is,
everyone has made alliances.

69
00:05:32,665 --> 00:05:36,252
If you think about hospitals
on par with QL Electronics' status,

70
00:05:36,335 --> 00:05:38,921
there is no better partner
than Sangkook University Hospital

71
00:05:39,005 --> 00:05:40,715
among the Big Five.

72
00:05:40,798 --> 00:05:43,801
That's true. QL and Hwajeong.

73
00:05:45,511 --> 00:05:47,638
Although Hwajeong
is not in the cell phone business,

74
00:05:48,598 --> 00:05:50,391
we're fighting tooth and nail

75
00:05:50,475 --> 00:05:52,435
in other business areas
in the global market.

76
00:05:52,518 --> 00:05:55,605
You are right. Hwajeong
is not in the cell phone business,

77
00:05:56,439 --> 00:05:58,900
and QL Electronics
does not own a hospital.

78
00:06:04,614 --> 00:06:05,573
